**story**
Once upon a time in a forest there lived a monkey who lived on a burried tree which was on the bank of a river in the same forest which the crocodile and his wife 
so one day the crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested under the tree the kind hearted monkey offered him so fruit the crocodile came back the next day for more fruits as he loved them as the days passed by
the crocodile and the monkey became good friends  